11#include "ipf.h"
12
13
14void binprint(ptr, size)
15 void *ptr;
16 size_t size;
17{
18 u_char *s;
19 int i, j;
20
21 for (i = size, j = 0, s = (u_char *)ptr; i; i--, s++) {
22 j++;
23 printf("%02x ", *s);
24 if (j == 16) {
25 printf("\n");
26 j = 0;
27 }
28 }
29 putchar('\n');
30 (void)fflush(stdout);
31}
32
